<i>no, no, no!</i>

05:56.482 --> 05:59.777
<i>Too many flies, too many flies</i>

05:59.860 --> 06:02.530
<i>but it's hot as hell in Philadelphia</i>

06:02.613 --> 06:04.657
<i>are you gonna open up a window?</i>

06:04.740 --> 06:06.700
<i>Can't we compromise here?</i>

06:06.784 --> 06:08.118
<i>Vote yes</i>

06:08.202 --> 06:10.371
<i>no, too many flies here</i>

06:10.454 --> 06:11.872
<i>vote yes</i>

06:11.956 --> 06:14.667
<i>oh, for god's sake, John, sit down</i>

06:14.750 --> 06:17.336
good god. Consider yourselves fortunate

06:17.419 --> 06:19.421
that you have John Adams to abuse,

06:19.505 --> 06:21.674
for no sane man would tolerate it.

06:21.757 --> 06:23.217
<i>John, you're a bore</i>

06:23.300 --> 06:25.177
<i>we've heard this before</i>

06:25.261 --> 06:27.638
<i>now, for god's sake, John, sit down</i>

06:27.721 --> 06:30.015
<i>- I say vote yes
- no!</i>

06:30.099 --> 06:31.809
<i>- Vote yes
- no!</i>

06:31.892 --> 06:34.061
<i>Vote for independency</i>

06:34.144 --> 06:36.146
<i>someone ought to open up a window</i>

06:36.814 --> 06:38.899
<i>I say vote yes</i>

06:38.983 --> 06:41.235
<i>sit down, John</i>

06:41.318 --> 06:44.029
<i>vote for independency</i>

06:44.113 --> 06:46.240
<i>will someone shut that man up?</i>

06:46.323 --> 06:47.950
Never!

06:48.993 --> 06:50.619
Never!

06:55.499 --> 06:56.750
Dear god.

06:57.960 --> 07:02.339
For one solid year
they have been sitting here. A whole year!

07:02.423 --> 07:03.924
Doing nothing!

07:04.842 --> 07:09.388
<i>I do believe
you've laid a curse on north America</i>

07:10.764 --> 07:15.394
<i>a curse that we
here now rehearse in Philadelphia</i>

07:16.353 --> 07:18.605
<i>a second flood, a simple famine</i>

07:18.689 --> 07:20.607
<i>plagues of locusts everywhere</i>

07:20.691 --> 07:22.568
<i>or a cataclysmic earthquake</i>

07:22.651 --> 07:24.611
<i>I'd accept with some despair</i>

07:24.695 --> 07:28.282
<i>but, no, you've sent us congress</i>

07:28.365 --> 07:32.703
<i>good god, sir, was that fair?</i>

07:34.621 --> 07:39.626
<i>I say this with humility in Philadelphia</i>

07:40.627 --> 07:45.299
<i>we're your responsibility in Philadelphia</i>

07:46.300 --> 07:50.637
<i>if you don't want to see us hanging
from some far off British hill</i>

07:50.721 --> 07:54.516
<i>if you don't want the voice of independency
forever stilled</i>

07:54.600 --> 07:58.020
<i>then god, sir, get thee to it</i>

07:58.228 --> 08:02.232
<i>for congress never will</i>

08:02.733 --> 08:05.402
<i>you see, we piddle, twiddle and resolve</i>

08:05.527 --> 08:07.571
<i>not one damn thing do we solve</i>

08:07.654 --> 08:09.740
<i>piddle, twiddle and resolve</i>

08:09.823 --> 08:11.575
<i>nothing's ever solved</i>

08:11.658 --> 08:15.162
<i>in foul, fetid, fuming, foggy, filthy</i>

08:15.245 --> 08:17.539
<i>Philadelphia</i>

08:17.790 --> 08:20.959
<i>someone ought to open up a window</i>

08:21.043 --> 08:22.711
shut up.

08:23.754 --> 08:27.383
<i>I now call congress' attention
to the petition of Mr. melchior meng,</i>

08:27.466 --> 08:30.552
<i>who claims $20 compensation
for his dead mule.</i>

08:30.636 --> 08:33.179
<i>It seems the animal was employed
transporting luggage</i>

08:33.263 --> 08:34.681
<i>in the service of congress.</i>

08:34.765 --> 08:37.893
<i>The question, then,
would appear to be one of occasion.</i>

08:37.976 --> 08:41.605
<i>For if the mule expired not while carrying,</i>

08:41.938 --> 08:43.941
<i>but after being unloaded,</i>

08:44.191 --> 08:47.444
<i>then clearly the beast dropped dead
on its own time.</i>

08:47.903 --> 08:49.822
Oh, good god.

08:51.448 --> 08:56.203
<i>They may sit here for years and years
in Philadelphia</i>

08:57.496 --> 09:02.251
<i>these indecisive grenadiers of Philadelphia</i>

09:03.085 --> 09:07.423
<i>they can't agree on what is right and wrong
or what is good or bad</i>

09:07.589 --> 09:11.009
<i>I'm convinced the only purpose
this congress ever had</i>

09:11.135 --> 09:14.388
<i>was to gather here specifically</i>

09:14.471 --> 09:17.808
<i>to drive John Adams mad!</i>

09:18.350 --> 09:21.061
<i>You see, we piddle, twiddle and resolve</i>

09:21.145 --> 09:22.938
