09:25.149 --> 09:26.650
<i>nothing's ever solved</i>

09:26.859 --> 09:30.070
<i>in foul, fetid, fuming, foggy, filthy</i>

09:30.154 --> 09:31.155
<i>Philadelphia</i>

09:31.280 --> 09:32.739
<i>John, john</i>

09:32.823 --> 09:37.202
<i>ls that you carrying on, John?</i>

09:38.328 --> 09:42.833
Abigail, Abigail, I have such a desire
to knock heads together.

09:42.916 --> 09:45.419
<i>Then why
in heaven's name do you stay there?</i>

09:45.502 --> 09:48.589
<i>Come home to Boston, John.
It's only 300 miles.</i>

09:48.672 --> 09:51.258
<i>If you left tonight,
you could be here in only eight days.</i>

09:51.341 --> 09:53.635
How can I do that, Abigail?

09:53.719 --> 09:57.264
I'm no further along now than I was
when I first came here.

09:57.347 --> 09:59.266
I know, my dearest. I know.

09:59.349 --> 10:02.311
But that's because you make
everything so complicated.

10:02.394 --> 10:04.146
It's all quite simple, really.

10:04.480 --> 10:07.441
<i>Just tell the congress to declare</i>

10:07.524 --> 10:10.819
<i>independency</i>

10:10.903 --> 10:13.071
<i>then sign your name get out of there</i>

10:13.155 --> 10:16.742
<i>and hurry home to me</i>

10:16.825 --> 10:19.495
<i>our children all have dysentery</i>

10:19.578 --> 10:21.705
<i>little tom keeps turning blue</i>

10:21.788 --> 10:23.707
<i>little Abby has the measles</i>

10:23.790 --> 10:26.043
<i>and I'm coming down with flu</i>

10:26.126 --> 10:29.129
<i>they say we may get smallpox</i>

10:29.213 --> 10:31.840
madam, what else is new?

10:35.302 --> 10:37.095
Abigail, in my last letter, I wrote you

10:37.179 --> 10:41.850
that the king had collected 12,000
German mercenaries to send against us.

10:41.934 --> 10:46.438
I asked you to organize the ladies
to make saltpeter for gunpowder.

10:46.855 --> 10:49.441
- Now, have you done as I asked?
- No, John, I have not.

10:49.525 --> 10:51.109
Well, why have you not?

10:51.193 --> 10:54.363
Because you neglected
to tell us how saltpeter is made.

10:54.905 --> 10:58.408
By treating sodium nitrate
with potassium chloride, of course.

10:58.492 --> 10:59.826
Oh, yes, of course.

10:59.910 --> 11:01.036
Will it be done, then?

11:01.370 --> 11:03.872
John, I'm afraid
we have a more urgent problem.

11:03.956 --> 11:05.624
More urgent, madam?

11:05.999 --> 11:10.254
<i>There's one thing every woman's missed
in Massachusetts bay</i>

11:12.381 --> 11:14.758
<i>don't smirk at me, you egotist</i>

11:14.883 --> 11:18.637
<i>pay heed to what I say</i>

11:18.720 --> 11:21.098
<i>we've gone from framingham to Boston</i>

11:21.181 --> 11:23.058
<i>and we cannot find a pin</i>

11:23.725 --> 11:27.646
<i>"don't you know there's a war on"
say the tradesmen with a grin</i>

11:27.729 --> 11:32.317
<i>well, we will not make saltpeter</i>

11:32.401 --> 11:36.572
<i>until you send us pins</i>

11:36.697 --> 11:38.824
pins, madam? Saltpeter.

11:38.907 --> 11:40.951
- Pins.
- Saltpeter.

