Done, madam, done.

11:54.423 --> 11:55.799
Done, John.

11:57.009 --> 11:59.303
Hurry home, John.

11:59.386 --> 12:00.554
As soon as I'm able.

12:00.637 --> 12:02.514
Don't stop writing. It's all I have.

12:02.598 --> 12:04.766
Every day, my dearest friend.

