20:04.120 --> 20:05.890
<i>- Here a Lee, there a Lee
- here a Lee, there a Lee</i>

20:05.914 --> 20:06.915
<i>when do you leave?</i>

20:06.998 --> 20:08.041
<i>Immediate-Lee!</i>

20:08.124 --> 20:10.061
<i>- Here a Lee, there a Lee
- here a Lee, there a Lee</i>

20:10.085 --> 20:11.211
<i>when will you return?</i>

20:11.294 --> 20:12.295
<i>Short-Lee!</i>

20:12.378 --> 20:14.190
<i>- Here a Lee, there a Lee
- here a Lee, there a Lee</i>

20:14.214 --> 20:16.216
<i>and I'll come back triumphant-Lee!</i>

20:16.299 --> 20:18.510
<i>Here a Lee, there a Lee</i>

20:18.593 --> 20:20.428
<i>everywhere a Lee, a Lee</i>

20:20.512 --> 20:22.388
<i>forward</i>

20:22.472 --> 20:28.269
<i>ho</i>

20:33.691 --> 20:37.862
That was the most revolting display
i have ever witnessed.

20:37.946 --> 20:39.823
They're a warm-blooded people, virginians.

20:39.906 --> 20:42.033
Not him, Franklin. You.

20:42.158 --> 20:44.744
You and your infernal obsession
for deviousness.

20:44.828 --> 20:47.973
If you'd come straight out and asked the
man, he'd have been gone a half hour ago.

20:47.997 --> 20:50.291
Yes, and he'd have been doing us a favor.

20:50.375 --> 20:53.378
Cheer up, John. At this very moment,
our cause is again riding high,

20:53.461 --> 20:56.506
sitting straight in the saddle
and in full gallop for Virginia.

20:56.589 --> 21:00.760
<i>And our women are serene</i>

