<i>full-bosomed</i>

21:06.975 --> 21:11.813
<i>full-bosomed, benjy
everyone a queen</i>

21:12.438 --> 21:16.109
<i>why they are lees, damn it
lees of old Virginia!</i>

21:16.192 --> 21:19.195
<i>Yes, sir, by god, it's
here a Lee, there a Lee!</i>

21:19.279 --> 21:21.489
<i>C'mon, John, step lively</i>

21:21.573 --> 21:23.658
<i>- here a Lee, there a Lee
- here a Lee, there a Lee</i>

21:23.741 --> 21:25.511
<i>- everywhere</i> a <i>Lee,</i> a <i>Lee
