free men rather than to live slaves."

01:07:18.785 --> 01:07:23.749
Thomas Jefferson,
"on the necessity of taking up arms," 1775.

01:07:23.832 --> 01:07:25.000
Magnificent.

01:07:25.751 --> 01:07:28.837
You write 10 times better
than any man in congress,

01:07:28.920 --> 01:07:30.631
including me.

01:07:30.714 --> 01:07:32.799
For a man of only 33 years,

01:07:32.883 --> 01:07:36.470
you possess a happy talent for composition

01:07:36.553 --> 01:07:39.431
