01:11:30.662 --> 01:11:33.081
Jefferson! I know you're in there!

01:11:35.250 --> 01:11:37.377
Jefferson, are you finished?

01:11:39.337 --> 01:11:41.339
Well, is it written yet?

01:11:44.217 --> 01:11:46.761
Well, you've had a whole week, man.

01:11:46.845 --> 01:11:48.221
Is it done?

01:11:49.973 --> 01:11:51.433
Can I see it?

01:11:59.024 --> 01:12:01.544
"There comes a time in the lives of men
when it becomes necessary

01:12:01.568 --> 01:12:04.779
"to advance from that subordination
in which they have hitherto..."

01:12:04.863 --> 01:12:06.531
This is terrible.

01:12:07.198 --> 01:12:08.199
Where's the rest of it?

01:12:14.497 --> 01:12:17.876
Do you mean to say
that it is not yet finished?

01:12:18.793 --> 01:12:19.961
No, sir.

01:12:20.045 --> 01:12:22.672
