01:12:35.560 --> 01:12:39.105
Someday you must tell me how you did it.

01:12:42.150 --> 01:12:43.902
Disgusting.

01:12:44.819 --> 01:12:46.404
Look at him, Franklin.

01:12:46.488 --> 01:12:48.698
Virginia's most famous lover.

01:12:49.616 --> 01:12:51.284
Virginia abstains.

01:12:55.288 --> 01:12:57.123
Well, cheer up, Jefferson.

01:12:57.207 --> 01:12:59.185
Get out of the clumps.
It'll come out all right, I assure you.

01:12:59.209 --> 01:13:01.586
Now, get back to work.

01:13:02.337 --> 01:13:04.965
Franklin, tell him to get back to work.

01:13:05.048 --> 01:13:06.800
I think he's asleep.

01:13:09.886 --> 01:13:11.554
Wake up, Franklin!

01:13:15.892 --> 01:13:19.104
Hello! And whose little girl are you?

01:13:22.899 --> 01:13:24.693
John, who is she?

01:13:24.776 --> 01:13:26.194
His wife.

01:13:27.278 --> 01:13:28.446
Ihope.

01:13:29.990 --> 01:13:31.658
What makes you think so?

01:13:31.741 --> 01:13:33.618
Because I sent for her.

01:13:34.744 --> 01:13:35.787
You what?

01:13:35.870 --> 01:13:38.474
Well, it simply occurred to me
that the sooner his problem was solved,

01:13:38.498 --> 01:13:40.542
the sooner our problem is solved.

01:13:40.625 --> 01:13:43.378
That's good thinking, John. Good thinking.

01:13:43.461 --> 01:13:46.464
Madam, may I present myself? John Adams.

01:13:49.509 --> 01:13:50.635
Adams.

01:13:52.303 --> 01:13:53.680
John Adams.

01:13:54.973 --> 01:13:57.142
And Dr. Franklin.

01:13:59.436 --> 01:14:01.563
The inventor of the stove.

01:14:06.151 --> 01:14:08.987
Jefferson, kindly present me to your wife.

01:14:11.865 --> 01:14:13.867
She is your wife, isn't she?

01:14:13.950 --> 01:14:15.870
Well, of course she is.
Look at the way they fit.

01:14:18.997 --> 01:14:20.331
Come along, John, come along.

01:14:20.415 --> 01:14:23.084
- Franklin, where are you going?
- Come along, John.

01:14:23.668 --> 01:14:25.503
Come along where? There's work to be done.

01:14:25.587 --> 01:14:26.921
Obviously.

01:14:27.630 --> 01:14:30.717
Good god. You don't mean to say that...

01:14:31.968 --> 01:14:34.262
I mean, they're not going to...

01:14:35.055 --> 01:14:37.682
In the middle of the afternoon?

01:14:37.766 --> 01:14:40.185
Not everybody's from Boston, John.

01:14:41.352 --> 01:14:43.104
Incredible.

01:14:43.188 --> 01:14:44.939
Well, goodbye, John.

01:14:45.857 --> 01:14:47.358
