01:16:36.593 --> 01:16:38.052
So you wrote.

01:16:39.804 --> 01:16:41.222
Tom and little Abby.

01:16:41.764 --> 01:16:44.142
Only now it's Quincy and Charles.

01:16:46.561 --> 01:16:49.814
And it appears the farm here
in braintree is failing, John.

01:16:51.191 --> 01:16:53.943
