01:20:03.883 --> 01:20:05.009
Well, as the French say...

01:20:05.093 --> 01:20:07.136
Please, Franklin!

01:20:07.220 --> 01:20:10.556
Spare me your bawdy mind
first thing in the morning.

01:20:11.766 --> 01:20:12.850
Dare we call?

01:20:13.059 --> 01:20:15.269
A congressman dares anything.

01:20:15.353 --> 01:20:17.188
- Go ahead.
